        Paska allows people to donate to restaurants in areas of need, so that they can continue to feed their communities and stay open post-war. 
        Currently, we are supporting Ukraine but in the future, we hope to help other countries. 
        Restaurants can submit a form to be featured on our website, and users can choose how much they want to donate. Instead of donating through a third-party, donate directly to the source. 
